C.T.C. Dealer Holdings Ltd said itextended its previously announced offer for 49 pct of &lt;CanadianTire Corp Ltd> to midnight on March 26.    CTC, a group of Canadian Tire dealers, which already owns17 pct of Canadian Tire, is currently appealing in an Ontariocourt against a previously announced Ontario SecuritiesCommission ruling blocking CTC's 272 mln dlr bid.    The blocked bid did not include non-voting shareholders,who hold 96 pct of Canadian Tire equity. Reuter&#3;